title: Harmonized Index of Consumer Prices: Liquid Fuels and Fuels and Lubricants for Personal Transport Equipment for European Union (27 countries from 2020)
notes:
The Harmonized Index of Consumer Prices category Liquid Fuels and Fuels and Lubricants for Personal Transport Equipment (FUELS) is a classification of nondurable goods and energy that includes Liquid Fuels (04.5.3) and Fuels and Lubricants for Personal Transport Equipment (07.2.2).

Information provided in the notes pertaining to Special Aggregates HICP classifications can be found from the source here (https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/cache/metadata/en/prc_hicp_esms.htm).
